{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/play-framework/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Edward Elric's Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"2a187629-4d24-563f-8960-4150b1f0ae19","excerpt":"安裝 Activator 先下載Activator\n解壓到\n將加到環境變量 Path 中\n在你的項目目錄中執行以下命令，驗證是否安裝成功 創建 Play 項目 安裝 Eclipse 插件 Scala IDE\n在 Eclipse 中 Install New Software 增加宰割 Update Site…","html":"<h2>安裝 Activator</h2>\n<p>先下載<a href=\"http://www.typesafe.com/community/core-tools/activator-and-sbt\">Activator</a>\n解壓到<code class=\"language-text\">D:\\Program Files\\activator-1.3.2</code>\n將<code class=\"language-text\">D:\\Program Files\\activator-1.3.2</code>加到環境變量 Path 中\n在你的項目目錄中執行以下命令，驗證是否安裝成功</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">activator -help</code></pre></div>\n<h2>創建 Play 項目</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">activator new demo play-java\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">cd</span> demo\nactivator</code></pre></div>\n<h2>安裝 Eclipse 插件</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://scala-ide.org/download/current.html\">Scala IDE</a>\n在 Eclipse 中 Install New Software 增加宰割 Update Site，記得安裝 Play Support</p>\n<h2>創建 Eclipse 項目</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">eclipse with-source<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>true</code></pre></div>\n<h2>跑起來看看</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">run</code></pre></div>\n<p>在瀏覽器中打開<a href=\"http://localhost:9000\">http://localhost:9000</a>，項目就跑起來了 ╰(￣ ▽ ￣)╮</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Play Framework項目初始化","date":"2015-05-23T00:00:00.000Z"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/play-framework/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/work-experience/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"工作心得"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/java8-installation/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Ubuntu安裝java8"}}}}}